[SHORT DESC]
Prevents Steel-type Pokémon from switching. Increases the chance of encountering a Steel-type Pokémon in the wild.
[LONG DESC]
<p>Steel-type enemy Pokémon cannot switch out.</p>

<p>A Steel-type Pokémon can escape by using Baton Pass or U-turn, or by holding the item Shed Shell.</p>

<p>When a Pokémon with this ability is first in the party, wild encounters with Steel-type Pokémon have a higher chance of occuring.</p>